{"tid":2025392,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【飛虎之雷霆極戰】汪明荃爆《野蠻奶奶》原有第3輯　黃宗澤被阿姐「詐型」嚇到一額汗","createTime":"2020-05-20T08:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T07:57:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37480202f98bdeca953bfbaa86e2ba55592f6131","tid":2025392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"由黃宗澤、吳卓羲及馬國明等人主演的《飛虎之雷霆極戰》播出，邵氏亦為劇集製作特備節目《飛虎同學會》。第2集邀來重量級嘉賓阿姐汪明荃，與黃宗澤、吳卓羲、陳山聰及主持錢嘉樂、陳敏之大談拍攝往事。<br />\n<br />\n黃宗澤（Bosco）、吳卓羲及陳山聰曾分別與阿姐合作拍劇，不過講到阿姐印象最深刻及最錫的小生就是「阿仔」Bosco，因他們曾與胡杏兒朝夕相對，拍攝了兩部劇集《我的野蠻奶奶》及《野蠻奶奶大戰戈師奶》。<br />\n<br />\n阿姐向Bosco「詐型」<br />\n阿姐在訪談中都非常關心Bosco與吳卓羲的感情狀況，更在Bosco派口罩套時趁機追問：「以為你派請帖，快啲啦！」令他一臉無奈，非常搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n之後，阿姐又提起與Bosco拍攝兩輯《野蠻奶奶》的趣事，指拍《野蠻奶奶大戰戈師奶》時每天的造型都不同，若要補拍就會重新襯衫，非常好玩。<br />\n<br />\n席間，阿姐表示原定《野蠻奶奶》有第3輯：「當時梁家樹想開一套黑色殭屍驚嚇喜劇，但是你搞垮了這個配搭，我覺得成數是很高的，我還以為可以演殭屍奶奶！」<br />\n<br />\n阿姐向Bosco「詐型」，笑指他與胡杏兒分手，令3人組合未能再拍劇，令Bosco嚇得一額汗，非常搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n阿姐大讚山聰<br />\n除向Bosco發功外，阿姐又問吳卓羲有沒有女朋友，不過他就指仍在靜待緣分的來臨。阿姐都藉機分享自己與家英哥都是21年才結婚，所以要有緣分是對的。<br />\n<br />\n此外，阿姐又大讚現時的陳山聰與昔日完全是兩個樣子，非常成熟穩重。陳山聰就指功勞都是來自太太Apple，並指太太一直在身邊扶持，對他的過去完全不介意，令他大為感動，並稱未來會努力工作，做好丈夫及「陳爸」的角色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2648062/Wong_thumb_20200520_cc_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2648062%2FWong_thumb_20200520_cc_1024.jpg&h=de5b2bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2648062/20200520wang1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2648062%2F20200520wang1_1024.jpg&h=5f45a31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2648062/20200520wang3_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2648062%2F20200520wang3_1024.PNG&h=24db9b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2648062/20200520wang2_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2648062%2F20200520wang2_1024.PNG&h=f94d42c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec172d91375d6c1527ab18d9e06de39f302104ad","tid":2025392,"uid":3172,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"lm睇gif"},{"pid":"b3a11548a2207f3482a866d6d4db2f17b63da434","tid":2025392,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"但是你搞垮了這個配搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540a36121cbd2707be62fcaa2b5f1bea8269a8dd","tid":2025392,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCdEHqp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCdEHqp.gif&h=afb3860e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b9ffa213d2ed9c50d3739e8f3a3b825f8d1a789","tid":2025392,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pSAjgTN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpSAjgTN.gif&h=9df6c317&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ea6a09e903e07f39b192993f514b655e7b90106","tid":2025392,"uid":115250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uA9v25e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuA9v25e.gif&h=3d074df4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uxh19Lj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxh19Lj.gif&h=55e25431&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e10db0152d18f0f5839526211d00ae489ed05e1","tid":2025392,"uid":27597,"lik